725240f-a.text:
35th Street (right, along cemetery and row of two family houses), south from 20th Road (formerly Old Bowery Road; left foreground), and 21st Ave., showing at the corner the private cemetery of the Lawrence family.

725097f-c.text:

March 1923.
Views 2 & 3: March 1925.
View 4: May 1926.
Eugene L. Ambruster Collection.
